title: After Mubarak, Egypt Appears Ready To Elect Another Military Man
teaser: Military dictator Hosni Mubarak was removed from power 3 years ago. The man expected to win the presidential election Abdel Fattah el-Sissi led an on-going crackdown against the Muslim Brotherhood.
